Package ioformat

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistanceMatrixIO
    This class handles some basic IO operations for reading and writing the distance matrix from and to files in the format that is used throughout this library.
    FileUtil
    Utility methods for creating and copying files, so that it is not a problem when the parent of the target does not exist.
    IOARFF
    A class that implements methods for data load and persistence to and from the ARFF data format, as used in Weka (for cross-compatibility).
    IOARFFDiscretized
    A class that implements methods for data load and persistence to and from a modified version of the ARFF data format.
    IOCSV
    This class handles loading and persisting data in CSV format.
    SupervisedLoader
    A class that implements methods for labeled data load from possible multiple data formats.
